00:00:13.346 --> 00:00:14.114 align:middle line:84%
And I think many people
today don't know what

00:00:14.114 --> 00:00:15.214 align:middle line:90%
to believe anymore.

00:00:15.214 --> 00:00:17.184 align:middle line:84%
>> People are basically
going to keep on to

00:00:17.184 --> 00:00:19.953 align:middle line:84%
and tell them what
really happened.

00:00:19.953 --> 00:00:22.022 align:middle line:84%
>> So like something
is watching me.

00:00:22.022 --> 00:00:23.590 align:middle line:84%
>> We weren't given
all the information.

00:00:23.590 --> 00:00:25.725 align:middle line:90%
We weren't told the entire story

00:00:25.725 --> 00:00:34.367 align:middle line:90%
[ Music ]

00:00:34.367 --> 00:00:35.702 align:middle line:90%
>> And now the host

00:00:35.702 --> 00:00:37.871 align:middle line:84%
of the nationally syndicated
Coast-to-Coast [applause]AM

00:00:37.871 --> 00:00:42.742 align:middle line:84%
