to annihilate us,

00:08:34.546 --> 00:08:36.583 align:middle line:84%
you have got to take
some action.

00:08:36.583 --> 00:08:38.952 align:middle line:84%
You cannot say, "Oh,
he's just trying

00:08:38.952 --> 00:08:41.421 align:middle line:90%
to bribe us for rice and food."

00:08:41.421 --> 00:08:43.256 align:middle line:84%
You've got to do
something about it.

00:08:43.256 --> 00:08:45.191 align:middle line:84%
And we're not doing
anything about it.

00:08:45.191 --> 00:08:48.528 align:middle line:84%
Is anybody in Congress raising
this issue that you bring

00:08:48.528 --> 00:08:50.363 align:middle line:90%
up in one second later?

00:08:50.363 --> 00:08:52.298 align:middle line:90%
>> Do you have a delete button,

00:08:52.298 --> 00:08:54.968 align:middle line:84%
because I might lose my
temper in about 10 seconds.

00:08:54.968 --> 00:08:57.203 align:middle line:84%
>> Guys, do you have
a delete button?

00:08:57.203 --> 00:09:02.141 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah. George, I'm a historian
and my PhD, my specialization,

00:09:02.141 --> 00:09:04.978 align:middle line:84%
