00:09:22.829 --> 00:09:23.896 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:09:23.896 --> 00:09:25.298 align:middle line:84%
>> Throughout history
we have faced this

00:09:25.298 --> 00:09:29.636 align:middle line:84%
