00:25:51.750 --> 00:25:52.718 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:25:52.718 --> 00:25:53.151 align:middle line:84%
>> Because you can't
buy anything.

00:25:53.151 --> 00:25:53.952 align:middle line:90%
