00:26:06.398 --> 00:26:07.633 align:middle line:90%
>> Pandemonium.

00:26:07.633 --> 00:26:08.934 align:middle line:84%
>> We're really getting
depressing here, aren't we?

00:26:08.934 --> 00:26:09.901 align:middle line:90%
>> I know it.

00:26:09.901 --> 00:26:10.969 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's, that's
what I meant.

00:26:10.969 --> 00:26:12.170 align:middle line:84%
This is not a program
