00:26:12.170 --> 00:26:13.772 align:middle line:90%
to be smiling and it's not...

00:26:13.772 --> 00:26:14.840 align:middle line:90%
>> But it's making people aware.

00:26:14.840 --> 00:26:16.108 align:middle line:90%
That's why I...

00:26:16.108 --> 00:26:18.877 align:middle line:84%
>> Right. But I guarantee
you, one day, whether it's

00:26:18.877 --> 00:26:25.550 align:middle line:84%
from the sun or from a rogue
nation that sets off a nuke

00:26:25.550 --> 00:26:28.954 align:middle line:84%
that creates an EMP attack
on us, people are going

00:26:28.954 --> 00:26:29.721 align:middle line:90%
to say, "You know what?

00:26:29.721 --> 00:26:31.289 align:middle line:90%
I heard about this.

00:26:31.289 --> 00:26:34.126 align:middle line:84%
I heard that William
Forstchen talk about that

00:26:34.126 --> 00:26:36.428 align:middle line:90%
and I didn't believe him."

00:26:36.428 --> 00:26:37.863 align:middle line:90%
But it will be too late.

00:26:37.863 --> 00:26:39.531 align:middle line:90%
>> You know my fear?

00:26:39.531 --> 00:26:41.466 align:middle line:84%
A mob might be coming
up my driveway saying,

00:26:41.466 --> 00:26:44.202 align:middle line:84%
