this is all your fault."

00:26:44.202 --> 00:26:44.936 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:26:44.936 --> 00:26:46.004 align:middle line:90%
>> So...

00:26:46.004 --> 00:26:47.406 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, we know you're
taking care of it.

00:26:47.406 --> 00:26:49.341 align:middle line:84%
>> Wait. Well, we know that you
