00:26:49.341 --> 00:26:50.475 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:26:50.475 --> 00:26:52.911 align:middle line:84%
>> And -- let me segue
on that for a second.

00:26:52.911 --> 00:26:56.915 align:middle line:84%
