over that initial hump if we,

00:27:05.390 --> 00:27:08.393 align:middle line:84%
even at our state and
local areas, said, "Okay,

00:27:08.393 --> 00:27:10.362 align:middle line:84%
we're going to take some
communications here..."

00:27:10.362 --> 00:27:11.496 align:middle line:90%
>> Hmm-mm.

00:27:11.496 --> 00:27:14.666 align:middle line:84%
>> "...and proof it so
we can be back online

00:27:14.666 --> 00:27:18.537 align:middle line:84%
and directing, commanding
control."

00:27:18.537 --> 00:27:22.140 align:middle line:84%
How much easier it would be to
get through those first 30 days

00:27:22.140 --> 00:27:25.243 align:middle line:84%
and start getting ourselves
working together as Americans.

00:27:25.243 --> 00:27:27.212 align:middle line:84%
