panic within hours.

00:27:27.212 --> 00:27:27.779 align:middle line:90%
>> Huge.

00:27:27.779 --> 00:27:28.714 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:27:28.714 --> 00:27:32.884 align:middle line:84%
>> Huge. Paint the
scenario for me.

00:27:32.884 --> 00:27:35.987 align:middle line:90%
