consideration..."

00:27:40.959 --> 00:27:41.793 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:27:41.793 --> 00:27:43.128 align:middle line:90%
>> ..."an ultimate nightmare."?

00:27:43.128 --> 00:27:46.531 align:middle line:84%
