00:27:53.972 --> 00:27:55.173 align:middle line:90%
But that's electrical power.

00:27:55.173 --> 00:27:56.942 align:middle line:84%
>> That's electric and
not everybody has a well.

00:27:56.942 --> 00:27:58.910 align:middle line:84%
>> I was doing a radio
program a couple of years ago

00:27:58.910 --> 00:28:01.213 align:middle line:84%
out of Phoenix where
somebody called up,

00:28:01.213 --> 00:28:02.581 align:middle line:90%
was a little dismissive,

00:28:02.581 --> 00:28:05.317 align:middle line:84%
