00:28:08.053 --> 00:28:08.887 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:28:08.887 --> 00:28:10.155 align:middle line:90%
>> ...going down to 95 at night.

00:28:10.155 --> 00:28:12.023 align:middle line:84%
What happens if Phoenix
is without water?

00:28:12.023 --> 00:28:14.292 align:middle line:84%
What happens if Denver
is without?

00:28:14.292 --> 00:28:17.462 align:middle line:84%
Well, the entire United
States' water supply system is

00:28:17.462 --> 00:28:20.332 align:middle line:84%
