only for getting to you,

00:28:20.332 --> 00:28:23.001 align:middle line:84%
but for going away
and being sanitized...

00:28:23.001 --> 00:28:24.069 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:28:24.069 --> 00:28:25.437 align:middle line:84%
See, but most people
think when they turn

00:28:25.437 --> 00:28:28.106 align:middle line:84%
on their spigot the
water just pressures out.

00:28:28.106 --> 00:28:29.341 align:middle line:90%
>> Comes out, yes.

00:28:29.341 --> 00:28:32.144 align:middle line:84%
>> No. There's an electrical
plant there pushing it

00:28:32.144 --> 00:28:33.812 align:middle line:90%
out to the people.

00:28:33.812 --> 00:28:36.848 align:middle line:84%
>> So, as we run down this
nightmare scenario, water.

00:28:36.848 --> 00:28:39.317 align:middle line:84%
And then within three
to five days we'll start

00:28:39.317 --> 00:28:41.987 align:middle line:84%
to see massive outbreaks
