that's in your refrigerators

00:28:50.495 --> 00:28:52.264 align:middle line:90%
which are now starting to decay.

00:28:52.264 --> 00:28:53.498 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:28:53.498 --> 00:28:55.066 align:middle line:84%
>> It's in your markets
which are starting to decay.

