00:28:59.404 --> 00:28:59.971 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:28:59.971 --> 00:29:00.939 align:middle line:90%
>> Your medical.

00:29:00.939 --> 00:29:02.407 align:middle line:90%
This is the scary one.

00:29:02.407 --> 00:29:05.944 align:middle line:84%
Place a -- I'll bet at least one
person in our studio audience is

00:29:05.944 --> 00:29:09.381 align:middle line:84%
