days you're in trouble.

00:29:22.194 --> 00:29:23.595 align:middle line:84%
>> Oh, you're in
trouble, absolutely.

00:29:23.595 --> 00:29:27.199 align:middle line:84%
>> About 20% of Americans are
on some sort of anti-depressant

00:29:27.199 --> 00:29:29.401 align:middle line:84%
or mood-altering
drug, but about 1% are

00:29:29.401 --> 00:29:31.670 align:middle line:90%
on anti-psychotic medications.

00:29:31.670 --> 00:29:33.905 align:middle line:84%
What happens to them
within 30 days?

