The entire transportation
grid is gone.

00:29:37.375 --> 00:29:38.710 align:middle line:84%
Now there's debate
about how many...

00:29:38.710 --> 00:29:40.712 align:middle line:84%
>> You're not flying
planes at that point, right

00:29:40.712 --> 00:29:44.149 align:middle line:84%
>> No. But some people
say, "Oh, only 10 to 20%

00:29:44.149 --> 00:29:46.551 align:middle line:90%
