you break down.

00:29:51.289 --> 00:29:52.424 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:29:52.424 --> 00:29:53.124 align:middle line:90%
>> You're up a creek.

00:29:53.124 --> 00:29:53.925 align:middle line:90%
>> Sure.

00:29:53.925 --> 00:29:55.026 align:middle line:90%
>> And really, the only cars

00:29:55.026 --> 00:29:56.628 align:middle line:84%
that would function
are the real old ones.

00:29:56.628 --> 00:29:58.063 align:middle line:84%
>> I drew a lot of
my information

00:29:58.063 --> 00:30:02.033 align:middle line:84%
as to what would happen
drawing on examples of the Seige

00:30:02.033 --> 00:30:06.371 align:middle line:84%
