00:30:14.079 --> 00:30:18.016 align:middle line:84%
for non-combatants and people
were receiving two slices

00:30:18.016 --> 00:30:21.219 align:middle line:84%
of bread, of which a third
to a half of the content

00:30:21.219 --> 00:30:23.188 align:middle line:90%
of the bread was wood pulp.

00:30:23.188 --> 00:30:24.155 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, my god.

00:30:24.155 --> 00:30:25.657 align:middle line:84%
>> You know why they
were doing that?

00:30:25.657 --> 00:30:29.094 align:middle line:84%
Because when the person ate
the wood pulp, the bread, it...

00:30:29.094 --> 00:30:29.928 align:middle line:90%
>> They can't stand it.

00:30:29.928 --> 00:30:30.762 align:middle line:90%
>> ...swells up their stomach...

00:30:30.762 --> 00:30:32.030 align:middle line:90%
>> And they weren't as hungry.

00:30:32.030 --> 00:30:33.598 align:middle line:84%
>> They weren't as hungry
as they starved to death.

00:30:33.598 --> 00:30:35.200 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, what about this?

00:30:35.200 --> 00:30:38.970 align:middle line:84%
The power goes out and
