cooling, can't cool any more.

00:30:43.475 --> 00:30:45.377 align:middle line:90%
So we have meltdowns.

00:30:45.377 --> 00:30:46.645 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:30:46.645 --> 00:30:50.348 align:middle line:84%
