this of just stare back

00:31:11.069 --> 00:31:12.304 align:middle line:90%
and say, "Next question."

00:31:12.304 --> 00:31:13.738 align:middle line:90%
>> They don't want to answer it.

00:31:13.738 --> 00:31:16.241 align:middle line:84%
>> But as declassified, as
several have pointed out,

00:31:16.241 --> 00:31:19.611 align:middle line:84%
it's built -- suppose
