00:31:45.103 --> 00:31:46.604 align:middle line:84%
>> ...is the worse
possibility...

00:31:46.604 --> 00:31:47.172 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:31:47.172 --> 00:31:47.605 align:middle line:90%
>> ...for us.

00:31:47.605 --> 00:31:48.173 align:middle line:90%
