going out as a tough old World
War II trooper that he was.

00:32:41.593 --> 00:32:42.794 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:32:42.794 --> 00:32:44.963 align:middle line:84%
>> And I asked the nurse
one day, "If this happened

00:32:44.963 --> 00:32:48.900 align:middle line:84%
