00:56:27.384 --> 00:56:29.853 align:middle line:90%
But whenever there was tension,

00:56:29.853 --> 00:56:31.755 align:middle line:84%
everybody wanted
to go down there.

00:56:31.755 --> 00:56:33.123 align:middle line:84%
>> Do you remember the
Twilight Zone  episode?

00:56:33.123 --> 00:56:34.124 align:middle line:90%
>> It was one of the greatest.

00:56:34.124 --> 00:56:35.926 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, yeah, yes.

00:56:35.926 --> 00:56:36.726 align:middle line:90%
>> One of the greatest.

00:56:36.726 --> 00:56:37.794 align:middle line:90%
Scary times.

00:56:37.794 --> 00:56:39.496 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, we are in scary times.

00:56:39.496 --> 00:56:40.630 align:middle line:90%
But again, I believe we

00:56:40.630 --> 00:56:43.934 align:middle line:84%
as Americans can
transcend scary times.

00:56:43.934 --> 00:56:46.903 align:middle line:84%
We should not be
afraid of the future.

00:56:46.903 --> 00:56:49.473 align:middle line:84%
We should be embracing
the challenge

00:56:49.473 --> 00:56:51.842 align:middle line:84%
and getting ready
beforehand because, in fact,

00:56:51.842 --> 00:56:53.009 align:middle line:90%
the act of getting ready

00:56:53.009 --> 00:56:55.011 align:middle line:84%
for it can very well
prevent it from happening.

00:56:55.011 --> 00:56:56.146 align:middle line:90%
>> Instant poll.

