though it's $50 million?

00:57:00.884 --> 00:57:01.852 align:middle line:90%
Almost universal.

00:57:01.852 --> 00:57:02.619 align:middle line:90%
It probably is.

00:57:02.619 --> 00:57:03.887 align:middle line:90%
Almost everybody did that.

00:57:03.887 --> 00:57:05.188 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:57:05.188 --> 00:57:08.758 align:middle line:84%
>> Even if it never happens,
what great peace of mind.

00:57:08.758 --> 00:57:11.127 align:middle line:84%
>> Did you ever have your
house insurance lapse

00:57:11.127 --> 00:57:13.129 align:middle line:84%
and you know there's a
hurricane wandering above?

00:57:13.129 --> 00:57:14.498 align:middle line:84%
>> No, thank god,
I didn't have that.

00:57:14.498 --> 00:57:17.133 align:middle line:84%
>> That happened to me once,
and I'm staring at the ceiling.

00:57:17.133 --> 00:57:18.401 align:middle line:90%
There was no peace of mind

00:57:18.401 --> 00:57:21.071 align:middle line:84%
