We only need that insurance
policy the day after,

00:57:24.741 --> 00:57:26.076 align:middle line:90%
but if you don't have it...

00:57:26.076 --> 00:57:26.877 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:57:26.877 --> 00:57:27.711 align:middle line:90%
>> ...and you're driving...

00:57:27.711 --> 00:57:28.912 align:middle line:90%
>> You're up the creek.

00:57:28.912 --> 00:57:30.580 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, all American
should realize we need an

00:57:30.580 --> 00:57:31.381 align:middle line:90%
insurance policy.

00:57:31.381 --> 00:57:32.582 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, we do.

00:57:32.582 --> 00:57:34.618 align:middle line:84%
And other countries I
think would follow suit...

00:57:34.618 --> 00:57:35.452 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:57:35.452 --> 00:57:36.553 align:middle line:90%
>> ...if they saw what we did.

00:57:36.553 --> 00:57:38.855 align:middle line:84%
>> And it might even
dissuade the lunatics,

00:57:38.855 --> 00:57:40.223 align:middle line:90%
the outright lunatics in Iran

00:57:40.223 --> 00:57:43.260 align:middle line:84%
and North Korea --
don't even try it.

00:57:43.260 --> 00:57:45.762 align:middle line:84%
>> Right. And then
the next problem is,

00:57:45.762 --> 00:57:49.399 align:middle line:84%
since we've taken care of the
grid, now we've got to take care

00:57:49.399 --> 00:57:54.104 align:middle line:84%
