launch to hit us on land.

00:57:54.104 --> 00:57:55.405 align:middle line:84%
>> That's a foreign
policy and that's...

00:57:55.405 --> 00:57:56.273 align:middle line:90%
>> That's another issue.

00:57:56.273 --> 00:57:58.508 align:middle line:90%
>> ...we address aggressively.

00:57:58.508 --> 00:58:00.110 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, it is another issue.

